<p>Familiarize yourself with common interview questions and practice your responses. Here are some resources for preparation:</p>
<ul>
<li><a href="https://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=interview+questions+preparation" target="_blank">YouTube: Interview Questions Preparation</a></li>
<li><a href="https://www.glassdoor.com/Interview/index.htm" target="_blank">Glassdoor: Interview Questions</a></li>
</ul>
